Create a PHP program to compute the sum of the digits of a number.

code:
<?php
// Number
$num = 12345;
$sum = 0;

// Loop through each digit
while ($num > 0) {
    $digit = $num % 10; // Get last digit
    $sum += $digit;     // Add to sum
    $num = (int)($num / 10); // Remove last digit
}

echo "Sum of digits is: $sum";
?>

output:
Sum of digits is: 15
